    question: '<h3>How much do you know about text formatting with HTML elements?</h3>\n<p>Which HTML element is best used for "???" to properly display this code within a webpage:  </p>\n<p><code>&#x3C;???></code>\n.alert {\ncolor:red;\n}\n<code>&#x3C;???></code></p>\n',
